\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fcontent%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_23%2FPetition_99604.html&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6jBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=52fad1bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html</a><br />\n<br />\n其實直接google translate個page就識簽<br />\n不過都有手足整左圖文教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aoymGxV\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aoymGxV</a><br />\n<br />\n--&gt; 我簽了，然後呢?<br />\n只要我們能於12月25日前集齊約五萬個簽名 **我們便能出席德國國會的聽證會去作進一步商討。 **<br />\n<br />\n另一重點是能在當地製造迴響,掀起反共浪潮及令德國支持民主自由<br />\n德國是全歐經濟最強國家 帶頭作用強 香港人一齊去簽 打倒共狗 Danke sch&ouml;n!<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9USBrby.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9USBrby.jpg&h=b26cd5a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OrydtpU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOrydtpU.jpg&h=d3127b5a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"22421efcae95284be12a940b30a5a6a0f7ff0147","tid":1788744,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:45:58.000Z","msg":"Usd 岩岩急插左下<br />\n如果繼續回彈<br />\n應該有野睇"},{"pid":"093cb87130c6476dc0e93de0691dca8bd7cd2f85","tid":1788744,"uid":146024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死黑警食撚屎啦"},{"pid":"2b959975e6ba4a5f840389c09648628d7c429d49","tid":1788744,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:00:02.000Z","msg":"生生世世永不原諒黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}